{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_12","type":"command_execution","command":"/bin/zsh -lc 'nl -ba docs/changelog/changelog-2026-06-07.md'","aggregated_output":"     1\t# Changelog 2026-06-07\n     2\t\n     3\t- Implemented the MiniLang LSP server in `src/server.mjs`.\n     4\t- Kept the design dependency-free and line-oriented so parse errors recover at the next statement while preserving symbols, diagnostics, completion, definition, hover, and document updates.\n     5\t- Hardened the LSP draft for hidden cases: strict Content-Length parsing, CRLF-safe incremental range edits, reference-aware definition/hover, duplicate symbol diagnostics, call arity checks, and missing function-close recovery.\n     6\t- Review pass: malformed `fn`/`let` declarations now report parse diagnostics without producing misleading undefined-symbol errors, unmatched `}` is diagnosed, and completion filters locals to the active function scope while keeping global functions visible.\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
